body:
I wonder if this can be fixed in `WorkspaceLoader.queueModule(Path dir)` by checking if the input parameter is a folder or not

```java
    private void queueModule(Path dir) {
        if (!loadedPoms.containsKey(dir)) {           
            if (Files.isDirectory(dir)) {
                dir = dir.resolve(POM_XML);
            }
            moduleQueue.push(new WorkspaceModulePom(dir));
        }
    }
```
